    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName ref="pl0092">Dupplin</placeName> Aug. 27<hi rend="superscript">th.</hi> 1772.</dateline>
                <opener>
                    <salute>My Lord</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I beg leave to return my best thanks for the obliging reception I met with at
                        <placeName ref="pl0110">Athol House</placeName>. The <hi rend="underline">seeing</hi> of <placeName ref="pl1127">Dunkeld</placeName> afforded me very
                    sensible pleasure. I am sorry that my ignorance of its beauties in 1769 has so
                    justly brought my taste in question. I found nothing to be drawn
                    there as <rs type="art" ref="ar0100">your Graces, <add place="above">paintings</add>
                    </rs> &amp; <rs type="art" ref="ar0099">a drawing</rs> I
                    got from <persName ref="pe0582">Stuart</persName> deprived <persName ref="pe0345">my
                        Servant</persName> of the means of adding anything new.</p>
                <p>after seeing <placeName ref="pl0298">the Camp at Comerie</placeName> I took the
                    Liberty of ordering some respects to be done on y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                    Grace's Land by digging into one of the Graves. <persName ref="pe0581">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> M<hi rend="superscript">c</hi>Nabb the
                        schoolmaster</persName> is my instrument.</p>
                <p>I beg the favor of y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Grace to present my respects to
                        <persName ref="pe0577">the Dutchess</persName> &amp; family and am, my
                    Lord</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Grace's much obliged<lb/> &amp; most
                            obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>
                    </salute>
                    <signed>
                        <persName ref="pe0232">Thomas
                        Pennant.</persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    <handShift/>from <persName ref="pe0232">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        Penant</persName>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <placeName ref="pl0092">Duplin</placeName> 22<hi rend="superscript">d.</hi>
                    August</p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="underline">1772</hi>
                </p>
            </div>
